HEADWORD: Assegai
<hw>As"se*gai</hw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr></mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pg. <ets>azagaia</ets>, Sp.
<ets>azagaya</ets>, fr. a Berber word. Cf. <er>Lancegay</er>.]</ety>
<def>A spear used by tribes in South Africa as a missile and for
stabbing, a kind of light javelin.</def>⟦br⟧
